    "However, successful initiatives in this area remain a challenge for countries worldwide, especially during such public health threats and in vulnerable settings.The Eastern Mediterranean region (EMR) is distinctly affected by ongoing conflicts, political unrest and displacements.",
    "This has posed unique vulnerabilities during the COVID-19 pandemic not experienced in other parts of the world.",
    "Despite its unique characteristics, there is still a paucity of information concerning the patterns of multi-sectoral collaborations that exist in this region.",
